   <script style="display:none">
    (function () {
     var agent = window.navigator.userAgent,
         safari = agent.indexOf('Safari') >= 0,
         versionIndex = agent.indexOf('Version'),
         version = 0,
         // Returns null when healthy, undefined when localStorage is not supported.
         unlocked = localStorage.getItem('federateUnlocked'),
         // Site setting defined in site's environment.properties file.
         active = true;
 
     // Grab the Safari version number.
     if (versionIndex >= 0) {
         version = parseInt('' + agent.substring(versionIndex + 8));
     }
 
     // Global state for all other code in the page to use.
     window.janrainSafariRefreshDetected = active && safari && version > 5 && unlocked === null;
 
     // Provide console feedback when refresh is impending.
     if (janrainSafariRefreshDetected) {
         console.warn('[jsrd v1.0.1] JANRAIN / SAFARI REFRESH DETECTED!');
     }
 }());
   </script>

 DDO.hasLocalStorage = function(){
     isDefined = typeof(localStorage) != "undefined";
     if(isDefined){
         localStorage.setItem("test", "test");
         canRetrieve = localStorage.getItem("test") == "test";
     }
     localStorage.removeItem("test");
     return isDefined && canRetrieve;
          
 }

   <script>
    //  SITE DATA
     
     DDO.siteData = {
         siteID: 'statesman',
         siteDomain: 'statesman.com',
         siteVersion: 'responsive site',
         siteFormat: 'newspaper',
         siteMetro: 'tx: austin',
         siteMedium: 'newspaper',
         siteType: 'main: free',
         siteCMS: 'methode'
     };
     // PAGE DATA
     var isDwp = true;
     console.log("isDwp: ", isDwp);
     var isHome = isDwp && true;
     console.log("page Title:" + 'Statesman.com - Austin News, Video, Longhorns and Weather');
     var trimPageNameUrl = removeExtracharFromUrl('/');
             
     DDO.pageData = {
         pageFlow : "",
         pageNumber : '1',
         pageType : 'standalone page',
         pageIsDwp: isDwp // Necessary for bookmarklet purposes.
     };
     if(isDwp) {
         DDO.pageData.pageContentType = (isHome) ? 'homepage' : 'section front';
         DDO.pageData.pageMainSection = (isHome) ? '/'+'homepage' : '/';
         DDO.pageData.pageName = (isHome) ? '/' + 'homepage' + '/' : '/';
     } else {
         DDO.pageData.pageContentType = 'HomePage';
         DDO.pageData.pageMainSection ='';
         DDO.pageData.pageName = trimPageNameUrl;
     }
     
     DDO.pageData.pageTitle = 'Statesman.com - Austin News, Video, Longhorns and Weather';
     DDO.pageData.pageSiteSection = (isHome) ? 'home' : 'Online';
      
     if (DDO.pageData.pageContentType == '') {
         var pageName = DDO.pageData.pageName;
         var pageNameSplit = pageName.split('/');
         DDO.pageData.pageContentType = pageNameSplit[1];
     }
     
     DDO.pageData.pageCategory = 'Home';
     if (DDO.pageData.pageCategory == 'Error') {
         DDO.pageData.pageContentType = "Page not found";
     }
     DDO.pageData.pageSubCategory = '';
     
     if(DDO.pageData.pageContentType =='404'){       
         DDO.pageData.pageType="errorpage";      
         DDO.pageData.pageTitle="page not found";        
         DDO.pageData.pageContentType = "404 page";      
         URLArray = window.location.href.split('/');     
         DDO.pageData.pageName = '/404_page/'+URLArray[URLArray.length-1];       
     }
     
     if(DDO.pageData.pageContentType == 'weather'){
         DDO.pageData.pageCategory = 'weather';
         DDO.pageData.pageTitle = 'weather';
     }
     
     if(DDO.pageData.pageContentType == 'searchresults'){
         var aMetricsSiteSearchType, aMetricsSearchTerms, aMetricsNumResults;
         DDO.pageData.pageName = "/search-results/";
         DDO.pageData.pageTitle = "search results";
         DDO.pageData.pageMainSection = "/search";
         DDO.pageData.pageContentType = "search"; 
         DDO.pageData.pageSiteSection = "search";
         
     }
     if(window.gallerySectionFlag){
         DDO.pageData.pageContentType = "gallery: section"
     }
     // CONTENT DATA (contentViewType is set in access meter metrics)
     DDO.contentData = DDO.contentData || {};
     var contentTopics ='';
     
     DDO.contentData.contentTopics = contentTopics;
     var contentByline = '';
     
     DDO.contentData.contentByline = contentByline;
     
     DDO.contentData.contentOriginatingSite =  'statesman';
     DDO.contentData.contentID = '175685aa-2131-11e6-a0f8-5a9883613c4b';
     DDO.contentData.contentVendor = '';
     DDO.contentData.contentViewType = DDO.contentData.contentViewType || '';
     DDO.contentData.contentPublishDate = '20160613210700';
     DDO.contentData.contentUpdatedDate = '20160714150500';
     DDO.contentData.blogName = '';
     DDO.contentData.galleryName = '';
     var pageSubContentType = '';
     if(pageSubContentType == 'Post') {
         DDO.contentData.blogName = 'Statesman.com - Austin News, Video, Longhorns and Weather';
     }else if(DDO.pageData.pageContentType == 'gallery') {

 DDO.init = function(pubsub, dependentEvents) {
     // The following code defers loading the DTM library until after certain events have been fired,
     // namely janrain, mg2, and access meter.
     // Note: we need to add access meter to list of dependent events etc!
     DDO.dependentEvents = dependentEvents;// e.g. ['authn', 'authz'];
     setTimeout(function(){
         DDO.dependentEventCheck("TIMED OUT");
     }, 10000);
     if(dependentEvents.length == 0){
         DDO.utilities.triggerDTMPageView();//DDO.utilities.loadDTMLibrary();
     }
     
     pubsub.publish("DDO-initialized");
     console.log('DDO: ', DDO);
     console.log(DDO.pageData.pageName);
 }
 
 //Function to remove last alphanumeric chars from DDO.pageData.pageName url
 function removeExtracharFromUrl(urlPath){
     var urlArr = urlPath.split('/');
     if (urlArr.length > 3) {
         var urlArr_new = [];
         for (var i=0; i<urlArr.length-2;i++) {
             urlArr_new.push(urlArr[i]);
         }
         return urlArr_new.join('/') + '/';
     } 
     else {
         return urlPath; 
     }
 }
   </script>
   <!-- end metrics_complete_override block -->
   <script>
    DDO.interaction = {
 	init: function(pubsub, $){
 		// pubsubcutioner can use regex for event names, thus all interaction type events
 		// can be listened to assuming the data is correct.
 		pubsub.subscribe("site-interaction", function(event, data){
 			// data should be like: {element:"[widget clicked]",action: "[button clicked]"}
 			DDO.action("interaction.Website", data);
 		});
 	}
 };
   </script>
   <script>
    window.breakpointArray = [1230, 990, 748] ;
 DDO.breakpoint = {
 	init: function(pubsub, $){
 		
 		DDO.pageData = DDO.pageData || {};
 		if (typeof $ !== 'undefined') {
 			var columns = getColumnNumber($(window).width());
 		}
 		DDO.pageData.pageLayout = columns + " column"
 		DDO.dependentEventCheck('breakpoint');
 		
 		pubsub.subscribe("breakpoint", function(event, data){
 			DDO.action("pageLayoutChange", data);
 		});
 	}
 };
 
 function getColumnNumber(width){
     breakpointArray = window.breakpointArray || 0;
     if(breakpointArray === 0){
         console.log("Breakpoint metrics tag not included in Methode frameset. Cannot compute column widths.")
         return false;
     }else{
         threeColumn = breakpointArray [0],
         twoColumn = breakpointArray[1],
         oneColumn = breakpointArray[2];
         if(width<= oneColumn){
             return 1;
         }else if(width>oneColumn &&  width <= twoColumn){
             return 2;
         }else if (width>twoColumn &&  width <= threeColumn) {
             return 3;
         }else if (width>threeColumn){
             return 4;
         }
 
     }
 
 }
   </script>
   <script>
    DDO.gallery = {
 	init: function(pubsub, $){
 		pubsub.subscribe("gallery-secondary", function(event, data){
 			DDO.action('gallerySecondaryPhotoView');
 		});
 		pubsub.subscribe("gallery-opened", function(event, data){
 			DDO.action('galleryOpened');
 		});
 	}
 };
   </script>
   <script>
    DDO.relatedObjects = {
 	init: function(pubsub, $){
 		pubsub.subscribe("related-objects", function(event, data){
 			var payloadData = data || {};
 			payloadData.contentType = DDO.pageData.pageContentType;
 			DDO.action("relatedObjects", payloadData);
 		});
 		pubsub.subscribe("non-gallery-photo", function(event, data){
 			DDO.action("nonGalleryPhoto", {contentType:DDO.pageData.pageContentType});
 		});
 	}
 };
   </script>
   <script>
    DDO.breakingNews = {
 	init: function(pubsub, $){
 		pubsub.subscribe("breaking-news-banner", function(event, data){
 			DDO.action("breakingNews", {contentType:DDO.pageData.pageContentType});
 		});
 		
 		pubsub.subscribe("breaking-news-story", function(event, data){
 			DDO.action('breakingNewsStory');
 		});
 	}
 };
   </script>
   <script>
    DDO.comment = {
 	init: function(pubsub, $){
 		pubsub.subscribe('comment-submit', function(event, data){
 			DDO.action('commentSubmitted');
 			// data should be like: {element:"[widget clicked]",action:"click"}
 			DDO.action('interaction-click', data);
 		});
 		
 		pubsub.subscribe('additional-comments', function(event, data){
 			DDO.action('additionalComments', data);
 		});
 	}
 };
   </script>
   <script>
    DDO.socialShare = {
 	init: function(pubsub, $){
 		pubsub.subscribe("authn-social-share", function(event, data){
 			DDO.action("socialClick", data);			
 		});
 	}
 };
   </script>

                         sizes.push([1, 1]);
                     
                     mapping.addSize(
                         [1230, 1], sizes
                     );
                 
                 var conf = {
                     name: 'NPR01',
                     id: 'cm-ad-NPR01',
                     sizes: defaultSizes,
                     group: 'default',
                     adunit: cmg.adconf.adunit,
                     outofpage: false,
                     companion: false,
                     mapping: mapping.build(),
                     targeting: {
                         ad_slot: 'NPR01'
                     }
                 };
                 cmg.adconf.slotconf.push(conf);
                 var slot = harmony.defineSlot(conf);
 
                 
             });
            </script>

                     );
                 
                     sizes = [];
                     
                         sizes.push([300, 600]);
                     
                         sizes.push([300, 250]);
                     
                     mapping.addSize(
                         [1005, 1], sizes
                     );
                 
                     sizes = [];
                     
                         sizes.push([300, 250]);
                     
                     mapping.addSize(
                         [748, 1], sizes
                     );
                 
                 var conf = {
                     name: 'RP01',
                     id: 'cm-ad-RP01',
                     sizes: defaultSizes,
                     group: 'RP01-RIGHT-RAIL',
                     adunit: cmg.adconf.adunit,
                     outofpage: false,
                     companion: false,
                     mapping: mapping.build(),
                     targeting: {
                         ad_slot: 'RP01'
                     }
                 };
                 cmg.adconf.slotconf.push(conf);
                 var slot = harmony.defineSlot(conf);
 
                 
                     if (slot) {
                         
                         var bpMap = {},
                             activeBPs = [1005, 1230];
                         activeBPs.forEach(function (bp) {
                             bpMap[bp] = true;
                         });
 
                         
                         harmony.on('update/slots', function (bp) {
                             slot.enabled = bp in bpMap;
                         }, true);
                     }
                 
             });
        </script>
        <script style="display:none">
         googletag.cmd.push(function () {
                 harmony.one('ready', function () {
                     harmony.show.group('RP01-RIGHT-RAIL');
                 });
             });
        </script>
        <div class="RP02 cm-ad default" id="cm-ad-RP02">
        </div>
        <script style="display:none">

                     );

                     }

                     sizes: defaultSizes,
                     group: 'gallery-ads',
                     adunit: cmg.adconf.adunit,
                     outofpage: false,
                     companion: false,
                     mapping: mapping.build(),
                     targeting: {
                         ad_slot: 'PG02'
                     }
                 };
                 cmg.adconf.slotconf.push(conf);
                 var slot = harmony.defineSlot(conf);
 
                 
             });
        </script>
       </div>

 				                        &lt;p class='photoCaption'&gt;Southwest Key, the company that operates 16 shelters in Texas that house migrant children, has come under recent scrutiny as dozens of protestors gathered on their doorstep in east Austin in a means to end their detention centers Thursday afternoon July 26, 2018.                          cmg_ads_page_type: cmg.adconf.targeting.obj_type,

                     });

                         newrelic.addPageAction('cmg_ads_rendered', {
                             cmg_ads_render_time: performance.now() - pageload,
                             cmg_ads_page_type: cmg.adconf.targeting.obj_type,
                             cmg_ads_environment: cmg.adconf.targeting.environ,
                             cmg_ads_media_type: cmg.adconf.targeting.mediatype,
                             cmg_ads_adunit: cmg.adconf.adunit,
                             cmg_ads_adunit_level_one: 'Austin_NP',
                             cmg_ads_adunit_level_two: 'aas_web_default'
                         });
                     }, true);
                     harmony.on('slotRenderEnded', function (event) {
                         event.slot._loadstart = performance.now();
                     }, true);
                     harmony.on('slotOnload', function (event) {
                         newrelic.addPageAction('cmg_ads_load', {
                             cmg_ads_slot: event.slot._name,
                             cmg_ads_render_time: performance.now() - event.slot._loadstart,
                             cmg_ads_page_type: cmg.adconf.targeting.obj_type,
                             cmg_ads_environment: cmg.adconf.targeting.environ,
                             cmg_ads_media_type: cmg.adconf.targeting.mediatype,
                             cmg_ads_adunit: cmg.adconf.adunit,
                             cmg_ads_adunit_level_one: 'Austin_NP',
                             cmg_ads_adunit_level_two: 'aas_web_default'
                         });
                     });
                 }
 
                 
                 harmony.load.targeting(cmg.adconf.targeting);
                 harmony.load.breakpoints(cmg.adconf.breakpoints);
 
                 
                 if (cmg.adconf.breakpoints.length) {
                     
                     var currentBP = harmony.breakpoint();
                     cmg.adconf.targeting.breakpoint = currentBP + 'px';
                     googletag.pubads().setTargeting('breakpoint', currentBP + 'px');
                     harmony.trigger('update/slots', currentBP);
                     
                     harmony.on('breakpoint/update', function (bp) {
                         googletag.pubads().clear();
                         googletag.pubads().setTargeting('breakpoint', bp + 'px');
                         harmony.trigger('update/slots', bp);
                         harmony.show.group('default');
                         console.info('Ad System Update: Targeting key "breakpoint" changed to "' + bp + 'px"');
                     }, true);
                 }
 
                 
                 if (!window.janrainSafariRefreshDetected) {
                     harmony.show.group('default');
                     harmony.trigger('ready');
                 }
 
                 
                 if (window.moatPrebidApi && moatPrebidApi.slotDataAvailable && moatPrebidApi.slotDataAvailable()) {
                     moatPrebidApi.setMoatTargetingForAllSlots();
                 }
             });

   <script style="display:none">
    harmony.one('ready', function () {
         function append(msg) {
             msg = msg || '';
             log += msg + '\n';
         }
         function title(name) {
             log += '\n';
             log += name;
             log += '\n-------------\n'
         }
         var log = '/* -----===== Begin Ad Logs =====----- */\n';
 
         title('Ad Unit:');
         append(
             cmg.adconf.adunit || 'ERROR: Ad unit could not be calculated!'
         );
         if (cmg.adconf.adunitOverride) {
             append('WARNING: Ad unit override is active.');
         }
         
 
         title('Breakpoints:');
         append(
             cmg.adconf.breakpoints.length ? cmg.adconf.breakpoints : 'None defined'
         );
 
         title('System Targeting:');
         append(
             JSON.stringify(cmg.adconf.targeting, null, 3) || 'WARNING: None defined.'
         );
 
         title('Slot Configurations:');
         if (!cmg.adconf.slotconf.length) {
             append('WARNING: This page contains no ad slots.');
         }
         var slotList = [];
         cmg.adconf.slotconf.forEach(function (slot) {
          if (slotList.indexOf(slot.name) == -1) {
              slotList.push(slot.name);
             append(slot.name);
 
             append('. default sizes:');
             slot.sizes = slot.sizes || [];
             if (!slot.sizes.length) {
                 append('\tNone defined');
             }
             slot.sizes.forEach(function (size) {
                 append('\t' + size);
             });
 
             append('. group: ' + slot.group);
             append('. companion? ' + (slot.companion ? 'yes' : 'no'));
             append('. out-of-page? ' + (slot.interstitial ? 'yes' : 'no'));
             append('. targeting: ' + JSON.stringify(slot.targeting, null, 3));
 
             append('. size mapping:');
             slot.mapping = slot.mapping || [];
             if (!slot.mapping.length) {
                 append('\tNone defined');
             }
             slot.mapping.forEach(function (breakpoint) {
                 append('\tat width ' + breakpoint[0][0] + 'px, use sizes:');
                 if (!breakpoint[1].length) {
                     append('\t\tNone defined');
                 }
                 breakpoint[1].forEach(function (size) {
                     append('\t\t' + size);
                 });
             });
 
             append();
         }
         });
 
         title('System Information:');
         append('Methode tags version 3.11.0');
         append('Harmony version ' + harmony.version);
 
         log += '\n/* -----====== End Ad Logs ======----- */\n';
 
         console.info(log);
     });
   </script>
